cp|8|AT|
^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|Drury is a convention that lets a passed hand by responder show a limit raise. If you play Drury, then over ONE of a major, and you are a passed hand, then 2C shows a 3 card limit raise and 2D shows a 4 card limit raise. I don't care for it myself, but many people like Drury.|
